Lecture 02: head 標籤 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<title>Sample04</title>　<!--文檔標題會顯示在網頁的分列-->
<style>
body{font-size: 20px}　/*定義 CSS 樣式（註解格式不同）*/
</style>
</head>

<body>
Hello World!
</body>
</html>

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<title>Sample05</title>
<base href="https://www.facebook.com/" target="_blank">　<!--base為所有連結之預設位址-->
</head>

<body>
Hello World!
<a href="samuel.chen.925">這是我的臉書</a>　<!--附加於 base 之後的網址內容-->
</body>
</html>
